title: [Giveaway Approval] - Celebrating SURE launch on BSC
body:
We would like to celebrate our launch on BSC with a Giveaway.
In order to get better exposure, we will launch this Giveaway in partnership with BNBSwap (https://twitter.com/BNBSwap 25.8k followers)

$500 worth $SURE (approximately 56818 SURE) #GIVEAWAY
10 Lucky Winners will get $50 worth #SURE Each
REQUIREMENTS:
1. Follow @InsureToken & @BNBSwap
2. Like & Retweet
3. Tag 3 Friends
4. Comment your #BSC Wallet Address
